Package com.salesforce.omakase.plugin.syntax

Plugins related to standard syntax refinement parsing.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeclarationPlugin
    Refines Declarations.
    FontFacePlugin
    Refines font-face at-rules (@font-face).
    KeyframesPlugin
    Refines keyframes at-rules (@keyframes).
    LinearGradientPlugin
    Refines RawFunctions to LinearGradientFunctionValues.
    MediaPlugin
    Refines media query at-rules (@media).
    SelectorPlugin
    Refines Selectors.
    SupportsPlugin
    Refines (generically) the supports at-rule (@supports).
    UnquotedIEFilterPlugin
    This plugin enables unquoted IE proprietary filters.
    UrlPlugin
    Refines RawFunctions to UrlFunctionValues.
